title: United Kingdom Imports of Iron & Steel
description: Imports of Iron & Steel in the United Kingdom decreased to 427.98 GBP Million in September from 488.89 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Iron & Steel in the United Kingdom averaged 347.81 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 631.75 GBP Million in March of 2011 and a record low of 148.20 GBP Million in December of 2001. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Iron & Steel.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
